Thank you.

723
01:31:30,958 --> 01:31:35,588
- The Mutant Registration Act
continues to draw support...
-[ Storm ] Mystique.

724
01:31:37,932 --> 01:31:41,231
[ Cyclops ]
Son of a bitch.

725
01:31:41,302 --> 01:31:43,270
from many
Parents Rights groups...

726
01:31:43,337 --> 01:31:47,068
