mutants in their school systems.

727
01:31:47,141 --> 01:31:49,769
In a related story,

728
01:31:49,844 --> 01:31:54,281
the body of Senator Kelly's longtime
aide, Henry Guyrich, was found today.

729
01:31:54,348 --> 01:31:59,615
Preliminary coroner reports
seem to indicate that Guyrich
was mauled by a bear.

730
01:31:59,687 --> 01:32:01,416
[ Rogue ]
Hey.

731
01:32:05,860 --> 01:32:09,318
- You running again ?
- No, not really.

732
01:32:10,998 --> 01:32:14,126
I have some things
to take care of up north.

733
01:32:19,607 --> 01:32:21,768
I kind of like it.

734
01:32:24,945 --> 01:32:28,403
- I don't want you to go.
- [ Sniffles ]

735
01:32:40,928 --> 01:32:42,919
I'll be back for this.

736
01:33:22,036 --> 01:33:24,561
Doesn't it ever wake you
in the middle of the night ?

737
01:33:24,638 --> 01:33:27,505
The feeling that someday
they will pass that foolish law...

738
01:33:27,575 --> 01:33:31,909
or one just like it
and come for you...

739
01:33:31,979 --> 01:33:34,846
and your children ?

740
01:33:37,084 --> 01:33:39,348
It does, indeed.

741
01:33:44,658 --> 01:33:47,684
What do you do when
you wake up to that ?

742
01:33:47,761 --> 01:33:50,924
I feel a great swell of pity
for the poor soul...

743
01:33:50,998 --> 01:33:54,661
who comes to that school
looking for trouble.

744
01:34:02,743 --> 01:34:05,371
Why do you come here,
Charles ?

745
01:34:05,446 --> 01:34:08,438
Why do you ask questions
to which you already know the answers ?

746
01:34:08,515 --> 01:34:10,949
Oh, yes.

747
01:34:11,018 --> 01:34:13,418
Your continuing search
for hope.

748
01:34:24,465 --> 01:34:28,765
You know this plastic prison of theirs
won't hold me forever.

749
01:34:28,836 --> 01:34:33,398
The war is still coming,
Charles, and I intend to fight it...

750
01:34:33,474 --> 01:34:35,442
by any means necessary.

751
01:34:37,278 --> 01:34:40,770
And I will always
be there,

752
01:34:40,848 --> 01:34:42,782
old friend.

